room_title: Escape room "A Very Tacky Christmas" by Tic Toc Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: This was a fun experience to do with my Nephews.  Evan was beyond accommodating to let us do the Christmas room.  I really appreciate the customer service and great time we had.  We will be back!

room_title: Escape room "A Very Tacky Christmas" by Tic Toc Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: Had an absolute blast! Will definitely be back as new rooms open! The owners couldn't have been nicer, good people!

room_title: Escape room "A Very Tacky Christmas" by Tic Toc Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: My fiance and I went there this afternoon and had a great time. We have tried several escape rooms and this one was more themed than any of the other rooms We have tried so far. The puzzles were clever and well thought out. Would highly recommend to anyone.
